[4] USA (Illinois, Kane County)
Date: Thu 30 May 2019
Source: Daily Herald [abridged, edited]
https://www.dailyherald.com/news/20190530/kane-county-confirms-local-case-of-measles-possible-public-exposure


Health department officials added Kane County to the list of communities affected by the largest measles outbreak in the US since 1994.

The Kane County Health Department confirmed a case of measles on 28 May 2019 and made the information public Thursday [30 May 2019] morning. The person is no longer infectious but visited several local retailers and restaurants during a period when the infection could be spread, the news release said.

[byline: James Fuller]

